        <div class="faq-q">My Cove is out of warranty — can you still service it?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes. Cove launched in 2019 and many LA machines are now 4–6 years old — at or past the standard warranty period. Out-of-warranty Cove service is a large part of what we do. We carry OEM Cove parts and service all models with the same quality and genuine parts as in-warranty work, at transparent flat-rate pricing.</div>
